reviews.text: We were attracted by the 25% off but my risotto were barely warm with the rice not thoroughly cooked. I finished the dish instead of sending it back because I had a meeting to go to early in the afternoon.
The restaurant is cozy and spacious. Food and service are good.
Good value for money, food variety with a twist

The food was mediocre, at most, however that wasn’t the lowest point of our experience here. Truth be told, the staff was the worst part of our short time in the restaurant. 

While we were ordering, the server misunderstood our order many times and asked in broken English for a clarification. We made it clear that our party was able to speak Cantonese, which would have helped very much but unfortunately the server misplaced a drink order and we had to call him back to clarify. 

Then, while we were eating our meals, the cleaners began cleaning at the restaraunt. That’s a good thing! However, they began cleaning the AC ventilation shafts—right above our table. The dust fell off the mop they were using and settled around us, and our table felt that this was a serious misconduct against health codes. 

Finally, instead of taking the bill, there were around 6-7 servers playing games on their phones by the entrance. This displays an unbelievable air of unprofessionalism that I wouldn’t expect from any establishment whatsoever.
blank face services, chewy pork knuckle

reviews.text: 服務員👉亞俊服務ㄧ流👍👍

中午套餐有好幾個Choice，選好後上菜時又可以互相share彼此ge喜好。
有頭盆，有湯，有甜品（係好美味超正雪糕）
下午四點多，人少的時候進去吃，服務員態度差，很不耐煩的樣，問他們德文"你好，歡迎，飲勝"點講，冇一個服務員答得出。食物一般，雪糕難食。冇下次。

沒有想過要寫食評所以沒有怎樣拍照。近來來這裡吃過幾次下午茶,這裡的食物任何一個環節都是敷衍中的敷衍,廚師沒有心煮,費時話時間詳述個情況,只能說,例如應該香煎的就全部水淥一淥就算，調味等detail位都是比人最廉價的茶餐廳的感覺，廚師只想快快出單。牛排亦沒有以前那麼好，醬汁都是亂調。

這裡的餐單設計亦都不同沙田分店，沙田的感覺上那邊的人真的懂得煮德國人的食物，地道高質，下午茶好低，這裡像是中國人扮懂得煮，但又其實不懂，像被港式茶餐廳化了，還拉低了質素。
我地訂左枱，6點鐘就入座。發現原來佢個happy hour 係做3-8pm,非常抵食。 而且佢個豬手口感一流，成班人一齊飲啤酒就最岩
